description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Mona Lisa / Leonardo da Vinci
-Madonna della Seggiola / Raphael
-The Last Supper / Leonardo da Vinci
-Bacchus and Ariadne / Titian
-The Wedding at Cana / Paolo Veronese
-The Peasant Wedding / Pieter Bruegel the Elder
-Annunciation / Fra Angelico
-Madonna of the Pomegranate / Sandro Botticelli
-Triumph of Galatea / Raphael
-Last Supper / Jacopo Tintoretto
